健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=a86e6756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.10"},{"pid":"dfda738228dd80f7cb9d3a2b5c7e5b15f3e1969e","tid":1558644,"uid":224860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"仲有屯門"},{"pid":"a52f060d58d99db30fcf335a00d81a5fa07cc751","tid":1558644,"uid":46703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"東涌呀仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bdd4f6f45f4dc6c3cb8c467d9a28fc477d9956","tid":1558644,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a52f060d58d99db30fcf335a00d81a5fa07cc751","tid":1558644,"uid":46703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"東涌呀仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b9baee2a3a614b154cfc877e6e8a8a7868f9cd","tid":1558644,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"